there's an ongoing debate about Rake tasks - see &lt;a href=&quot;/projects/8994/tickets/59&quot; title=&quot;Ticket #59&quot;&gt;#59&lt;/a&gt; for details.
This can probably be closed, and discussion moved to &lt;a href=&quot;/projects/8994/tickets/59&quot; title=&quot;Ticket #59&quot;&gt;#59&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that the patch given here will cause odd results if more
